{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1672772557.361556", "card_id": "Q_576523800", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 517}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "乐视宣布实行四天半工作制，周三休息半天，如何看待这一举措？会被推广吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "乐视视频官微宣布：2023 年 1 月 1 日起，乐视将执行每周四天半工作制，每周三弹性工作半天。乐视在公告中表示，连续三年的疫情难免影响公司业务，所有员工都关心公司业绩，也更担心自己的生活。让人欣慰的是，在大家的努力下, 公司 2022 年业务总体平稳，经营业务实现了现金流平衡，并且前 3 季度虽有 5 周居家办公，整体业绩目标均如期达成。 来源：贝壳财经"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-0e75495fae005665894e611ca1e59d7b_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "847 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/576523800"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I0fK2/OWIvaVJEAMaCDkwMzk3OTU1IOelz50GMFU41QpAAHIJNTc2NTIzODAweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1672772557.3625515", "card_id": "Q_576510658", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 498}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "阳康以后，你还感觉有哪些不适？用了多久才完全恢复到自己从前的状态？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-0bf90dfb4f20e6e6a676476f09d252c9_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "292 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/576510658"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I0fK2/OWIvaVJEAMaCDkwMzk1MDA2II7+zp0GMAs4uwlAAXIJNTc2NTEwNjU4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1672772557.3630328", "card_id": "Q_498058002", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.pn